Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.52,0:01:35.35,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shusuke Amagai was the one responsible\Nfor the string of disturbances.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.35,0:01:39.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,He did so in order to\Nassassinate Genryusai.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.52,0:01:42.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,He joined the Thirteen\NCourt Guard Squads
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.03,0:01:45.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,so that he could take revenge on\NGenryusai for killing his father.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.40,0:01:46.87,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,After long years of preparation,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.87,0:01:51.07,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Amagai waited for the moment when\Nthe Soul Reapers were dispatched
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.07,0:01:54.39,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,to put down the rebellion\Nby the Kasumiohji Clan,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.39,0:01:56.85,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,leaving few people\Naround Genryusai.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.56,0:02:00.33,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Amagai’s Bakkouto\Npossessed the power
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.33,0:02:03.73,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,to render the Zanpakuto of\Nthe Soul Reapers powerless.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.80,0:02:08.15,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,After rendering Genryusai’s\NRyujinjakka powerless,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.15,0:02:11.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Amagai used Bankai and attempted to\Nsettle the score once and for all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.94,0:02:14.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,However, Ichigo arrived and\Nstood between the two,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.04,0:02:16.11,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,whereupon an evenly\Nmatched battle ensued.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.77,0:02:20.25,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Only Ichigo, who possessed\Nthe ability to Hollowfy,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.25,0:02:24.53,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,was able to fight without suffering\Nthe effects of the Bakkouto.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.06,0:02:28.19,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,After an epic battle,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.19,0:02:31.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo’s Getsugatensho finally\Nstruck Amagai.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.39,0:02:40.14,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Getsugatensho!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.92,0:03:08.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,No… It can’t be.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.31,0:03:22.81,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it. It’s not over yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.37,0:03:25.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no end.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.40,0:03:29.27,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Until I accomplish my revenge…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.32,0:03:34.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it! You can’t do anything\Nin your condition!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.49,0:03:35.83,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,As I told you…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.60,0:03:39.97,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I will not find my answer\Nuntil I kill them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.60,0:03:43.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And beyond that…is death!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.90,0:03:51.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That’s…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.54,0:04:04.47,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.23,0:04:16.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it! If you remain like that, you’ll…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.57,0:04:58.49,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Gouen Ryuga, Homura!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.60,0:05:04.65,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.98,0:05:17.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You underestimated me,\NSubstitute Soul Reaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.75,0:05:25.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be? The Bakkouto has\Nnot taken control of him?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.55,0:05:30.33,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I am suppressing this with\Nmy Spiritual Pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.83,0:05:32.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It hasn’t grown, has it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.09,0:05:35.38,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re next…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.92,0:05:37.01,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Genryusai!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.33,0:05:44.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It appears you haven’t discarded\Nyour pride as a Soul Reaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.54,0:05:45.73,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Pride, you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.33,0:05:48.83,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You, who spoke of order\Nin the Soul Society,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.83,0:05:51.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,but eliminated those\Nwho did not follow your will?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.94,0:05:54.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t want to be lectured\Nby you, Genryusai!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.98,0:06:01.73,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I will take care of\Nboth you and Rurichiyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.17,0:06:04.29,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.97,0:06:23.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.64,0:06:26.51,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re still alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.13,0:06:28.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re a stubborn fellow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.32,0:06:33.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m your opponent!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.91,0:06:34.87,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.69,0:06:38.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Rurichiyo, don’t look so sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.94,0:06:40.37,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.41,0:06:43.17,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You should be dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.71,0:06:46.61,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you go to such lengths\Nto keep coming at me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.97,0:06:50.05,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,There’s no reason why you should\Nsave this old geezer!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.65,0:06:51.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, already!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.33,0:06:53.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.32,0:06:55.17,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know how many people you
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.17,0:06:58.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,made unhappy just for your selfish cause?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.54,0:07:04.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You used the Kasumiohji Clan,\Ntricked the Soul Reapers,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.04,0:07:06.97,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and got involved with the Bakkouto.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.32,0:07:09.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You think it’s all right\Nto do anything
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.44,0:07:11.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,if it’s for the purpose of \Ntaking revenge for your father?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.16,0:07:17.07,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You think the people who cried\Nbecause of you don’t matter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.25,0:07:22.89,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,In spite of the chaos that\Noccurred in the Kasumiohji Clan,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.89,0:07:26.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Rurichiyo made the firm decision\Nto shoulder that burden and live on!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.94,0:07:31.38,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Rather than run from her destiny,\Nshe chose to challenge it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.96,0:07:34.31,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,She’s not like you,\Nwho chose to run from yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.52,0:07:41.11,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m going to squash\Nyour stupid selfish revenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.93,0:07:46.59,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you do that\Nwith the strength you have?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.23,0:07:48.66,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I sure can!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.01,0:07:53.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you can hollowfy,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.57,0:07:56.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,it’s still a fact that your Soul Reaper\Npowers are neutralized.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.65,0:08:01.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That means you can’t bring out\Nall of your powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.03,0:08:03.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,So what of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.96,0:08:08.73,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn’t underestimate me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.83,0:08:11.57,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t get so full of yourself, kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.75,0:08:29.99,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}His speed has increased.\NIf that’s the case…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.61,0:08:34.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Gouen Ryuga!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.39,0:08:40.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Got him!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.27,0:08:50.11,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.72,0:08:51.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Homura!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.23,0:08:57.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.28,0:09:02.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Got you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.65,0:09:03.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,So that’s how…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.74,0:09:08.29,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That was how you blocked\Nmy first flame.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.25,0:09:11.37,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Though I haven’t perfected it yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.10,0:09:16.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Once I get the hang of it,\NI’ll cut down all your attacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.84,0:09:20.49,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I’ll end this before that happens!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.72,0:09:36.59,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.14,0:09:40.09,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll have to do something about\Nthe Bakkouto on his right arm, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.94,0:09:44.51,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He’s guarding his right side.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.06,0:09:48.59,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As I thought, his right side with\Nthe Bakkouto is weaker.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.59,0:09:49.47,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In that case…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.78,0:09:57.29,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}His movements have changed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.82,0:09:59.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He’s moving more broadly\Nfrom side to side,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.58,0:10:04.11,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}drawing my attacks with him and\Nreducing my attacks from the middle.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.73,0:10:05.25,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}However…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.06,0:10:08.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Raiendan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.69,0:10:19.38,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He attacked the ground to\Nconceal himself?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.32,0:10:22.05,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is he going to attack from there?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.37,0:10:24.70,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No, from the right.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.48,0:10:28.91,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Getsuga…tensho!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.74,0:10:30.71,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw that coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.25,0:10:34.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Getsuga…tensho!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.74,0:10:36.75,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.17,0:10:51.23,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.18,0:10:55.39,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Rurichiyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.77,0:11:15.67,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,How's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.00,0:11:18.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You can’t use that sword anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.67,0:11:22.89,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Curse you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.10,0:11:24.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,With this many injuries…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.44,0:11:29.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you defeat me and the old man,\Nyou won’t get away unscathed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.30,0:11:32.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s useless to fight any further.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.31,0:11:38.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Useless to fight any further, you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.00,0:11:44.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you at the start, this is a life\Nthat I’ve already discarded!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.08,0:11:48.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can have Genryusai’s head,\Nthat’s all that matters!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.51,0:11:55.83,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll take every one of\Nyou bastards with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.52,0:12:00.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, Amagai!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.47,0:12:03.01,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If you continue to feed it any more
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.01,0:12:05.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Spiritual Pressure in your condition,even you won’t…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.47,0:12:07.27,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I said I don’t care!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.79,0:12:12.79,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The only way to stop people who\Nwon’t listen no matter what I say
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.79,0:12:13.95,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,is to blow them away!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.09,0:12:16.91,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.49,0:12:18.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.54,0:12:19.38,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurosaki…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.94,0:12:22.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,For someone who became a captain,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.96,0:12:25.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nyou’re doing a foolish thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.57,0:12:27.67,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What would you know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.67,0:12:31.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Revenge is my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.84,0:12:59.82,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.86,0:13:15.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo won.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.42,0:13:16.11,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.35,0:13:24.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.99,0:13:26.77,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Curse you, Genryusai.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.57,0:13:34.29,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll get my father’s revenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.30,0:13:37.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, Amagai!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.94,0:13:52.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Master Genryusai!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.20,0:13:53.09,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Old Man Yama!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.09,0:13:54.25,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay where you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.05,0:14:00.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Amagai!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.06,0:14:04.11,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The Head Captain is not\Nyour father’s killer!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.11,0:14:05.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.26,0:14:09.75,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Your father was a victim,\Nswallowed up by the Bakkouto.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.81,0:14:17.39,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,As you know,\Nback then in the Kasumiohji Clan,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.39,0:14:19.91,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Gyokaku Kumoi misused\Nspecial techniques passed down
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.91,0:14:23.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,through the Kasumiohji Clan\Nfor casting gift swords
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.08,0:14:25.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,in order to develop the Bakkouto.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.27,0:14:28.67,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, using prototypes,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.12,0:14:31.33,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,he began experimenting on people.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.43,0:14:36.93,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,When Master Genryusai\Nbecame aware of this,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.93,0:14:39.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,he attempted to investigate, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.57,0:14:46.71,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Cease your intervention\Nin the Kasumiohji Clan.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.10,0:14:50.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Using their political immunity as a shield,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.58,0:14:53.83,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,he was denied permission to\Ninvestigate the Kasumiohji Clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.85,0:14:55.61,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,However…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.05,0:15:00.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Master Genryusai… Please allow me\Nto handle this matter.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.07,0:15:02.31,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kisaragi…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.19,0:15:06.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I shall find it and return\N with the secret of the{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.26,0:15:07.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}suspicious sword without fail.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.93,0:15:10.69,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinetsu Kisaragi…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.54,0:15:13.09,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,At the time, your father was\NMaster Genryusai's subordinate
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.09,0:15:14.01,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and an outstanding student.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.31,0:15:17.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Master Genryusai ordered him
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.03,0:15:20.29,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,to conduct an undercover investigation\Nin utmost secrecy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.37,0:15:23.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,However…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.36,0:15:30.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A Soul Reaper, huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.74,0:15:34.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well, well, you’ll make\Na valuable guinea pig.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.58,0:15:37.35,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Stop it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.54,0:15:45.97,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kill the person who sent you here!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.62,0:16:15.45,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Master…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.70,0:16:25.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Both parties could not reveal\Nthe truth about Kisaragi’s death.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.83,0:16:28.63,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,There was the secret of the Bakkouto,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.63,0:16:31.57,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and the undercover investigation\Nthat violated Central 46’s orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.91,0:16:37.66,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,As a result, Kisaragi’s death\Nwas kept hidden.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.96,0:16:42.98,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Master Genryusai seemingly repaired\Nrelations with the Kasumiohji Clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.87,0:16:46.65,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Those were probably\Nthe records that you saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.63,0:16:48.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Then…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.71,0:16:51.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,he killed my father because…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.24,0:16:56.93,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The torment Old Man Yama felt after\Nhaving to kill his own student…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.69,0:16:59.53,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you imagine what that was like?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.54,0:17:02.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,No way…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.22,0:17:09.57,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I was consumed by my hatred and\Nwas unable to see through to the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.83,0:17:13.37,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You, and your destiny itself,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.37,0:17:15.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,seem to have been consumed\Nby the Bakkouto.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.21,0:17:19.82,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Be careful of the Bakkouto.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.49,0:17:21.97,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Of the Bakkouto…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.62,0:17:31.70,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I did a terrible thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.74,0:17:35.97,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,So you’re Kisaragi’s son?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.83,0:17:38.47,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You are a lot like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.00,0:17:41.25,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Genryusai…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.00,0:17:44.82,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I was a shallow fool in all of this,\Nwasn’t I?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.17,0:17:47.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You need not be ashamed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.48,0:17:52.95,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive my failure to save\Nyou and your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.61,0:18:09.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What is he doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.00,0:18:11.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Byakuya…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.50,0:18:14.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shusuke Amagai still has\Nhis dignity to uphold.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.51,0:18:18.05,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,He is a man who became\Na captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.33,0:18:21.75,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Let him end his life\Nthe way he wishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.95,0:18:24.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.75,0:18:29.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for dragging you\Ninto such a trifling matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.99,0:18:33.47,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Amagai…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.93,0:18:38.49,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I enjoyed the time I spent with\Nyou and the men.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.90,0:18:40.82,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Farewell.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.02,0:18:46.55,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Amagai!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.55,0:19:14.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo… I am truly in your debt for\Nall you have done this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.65,0:19:17.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I owe everything to your people.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.90,0:19:19.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I am grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.72,0:19:21.47,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it. Don’t worry about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.37,0:19:23.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo Kurosaki…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.84,0:19:27.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to your efforts,\Nour clan avoided being abolished.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.72,0:19:30.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I thank you from\Nthe bottom of my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.06,0:19:30.99,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.34,0:19:33.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That was the first time you received\Na decent thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.62,0:19:35.43,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shu…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.04,0:19:38.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you be remaining\Nwith the Kasumiohji Clan, as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.39,0:19:39.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.98,0:19:45.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The wedding was called off,\Nbut I…you know…still like Ruricchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.34,0:19:48.23,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.42,0:19:51.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, I’m your fiancé…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.32,0:19:53.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But, are you sure about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.70,0:19:56.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Succeeding the Kasumiohji Clan\Nat your age…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.07,0:19:58.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I do not mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.58,0:20:01.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It is the clan everyone tried to protect.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.32,0:20:04.23,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And I have also made my decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.64,0:20:08.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re finally free of people\Ntargeting your life,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.85,0:20:11.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,but you’ll be unable\Nto play freely once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.68,0:20:14.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.88,0:20:16.70,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to you and the others, Ichigo,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.70,0:20:20.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I was able to fully experience\Nthe outside world, was I not?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.41,0:20:24.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I will never, ever forget\Nthe World of the Living
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.20,0:20:25.67,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and you and the others, Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.39,0:20:29.53,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If I have those memories,\NI will be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.23,0:20:33.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t worry, Rurichiyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.58,0:20:34.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If anything should happen,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.94,0:20:37.55,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,we’ll be the first to\Nrace to your side!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.18,0:20:41.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,No thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.22,0:20:41.98,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.08,0:20:46.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Having to borrow your help\Nwould mean
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.03,0:20:51.23,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,that the Kasumiohji Clan has committed\Nanother mishap like this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.88,0:20:58.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,There must never be another\Nunfortunate man like Shusuke Amagai.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.62,0:21:01.27,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That is my mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.52,0:21:03.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Rurichiyo…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.35,0:21:07.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The next time we see each other will\Nbe when I’ve accomplished that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.68,0:21:08.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that clear?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.38,0:21:10.17,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.10,0:21:12.71,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.52,0:21:20.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Farewell, Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.32,0:21:21.61,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s meet again!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.69,0:23:23.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m glad we managed to\Nget that out of the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.62,0:23:26.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to get back quickly\Nand report to everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.02,0:23:28.45,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I have somewhere to go,\Nso I’ll part with you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.45,0:23:29.49,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We’re in the middle of the Precipice World.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.49,0:23:30.47,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Where do you think you’re going?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.47,0:23:31.79,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,To prepare for the next episode\Nand beyond.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.79,0:23:33.09,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t have time to explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.41,0:23:34.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.99,0:23:36.57,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.96,0:23:38.37,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s see now…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.16,0:23:43.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back, Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.92,0:23:45.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you done dealing with\Nthe grown-up issues?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.16,0:23:47.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Nel?! You’re…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.42,0:23:48.93,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry, Kurosaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.36,0:23:51.41,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to use Bankai\Nand get over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.98,0:23:52.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Here?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.84,0:23:53.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.85,0:23:55.31,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we’re all set!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.53,0:23:57.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Inoue! What’s going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.74,0:24:00.82,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Starting next episode, we’ll be resuming\Nthe Hueco Mundo Arc!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.82,0:24:01.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.51,0:24:04.63,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,– I’m looking forward to it!\N– Huh? Huh? Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.63,0:24:06.63,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,